{"word":"G5412 - φορτίζω - phortízō - for-tid'-zo - Lade","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φορτίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phortízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">for-tid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lade</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுமத்து"},{"paragraph":"to place a burden upon, to load"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5414 - φόρτος - phórtos - for'-tos/5414\">G5414</a>; to <i>load</i> up (properly as a vessel or animal), that is, (figuratively) to <i>overburden</i> with ceremony (or spiritual anxiety): - lade, be heavy laden.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1308/1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313/1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2018/2018\">G2018</a>, <a href=\"#/G399/399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4374/4374\">G4374</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376/4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851/4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342/5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5409/5409\">G5409</a>, <a href=\"#/G5411/5411\">G5411</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412/5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413/5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414/5414\">G5414</a>"}]}